ownedComment.body: This attribute contains the No ALarM reporting Qualified Inhibit interval. Alarm Reporting is turned off until the managed entity is qualified problem-free for a specified persistence interval. Values between 0 and 5940 are allowed which identify an interval between 0 and 99 hours with a one-minute granularity.
